      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FIERY WORDS (5) lines up here off a comfortable win at this track after jumping from box 1 (23.91). Will need some luck early after drawing a tricky box here. Well placed and can measure up. DOZEN DONUTS (2) produced a modest effort most recently when sixth at this track over 407m behind Another Meghan (24.29) in a Grade 5. Was a winner prior to that. Deserves plenty of respect. SEEK TO FLY (1) has mixed form recently, finishing fourth (23.99) in a Grade 5 at this track latest but did run well two back when in the frame. This looks easier and expected to improve sharply. CLEAR BLUE SKY (4) hit the frame here last time and looks a chance again.",
